對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"c1363a9830b4eec65fd46ea24b3897514b3c1800","tid":1342930,"uid":17945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:21:35.000Z","msg":"緊急發起明天罷市罷工罷課！<br />\n理由是今晚元朗發生的事件，顯示香港政府及香港警察已經無能力保障市民生命財產安全！<br />\n<br />\n現呼籲全港市民發起三罷！<br />\n直至政府及警察為事件作出交代！<br />\n<br />\n包括：<br />\n<br />\n1）全數緝拿涉事兇徒歸案<br />\n2）全盤交代警力不足及遲遲不到現場原因，追究一切相關人事責任<br />\n3）因應有市民拍到立法會議員何君堯於事發前與疑似元朗黑道中人相約面談，要求徹查何於事件中的角色！<br />\n<br />\n以上三項，缺一回應，堅持無限期三罷！<br />\n<br />\n(*請複製上文廣傳轉發"},{"pid":"0cc3a97a0a2e7e4b680308da2c6bfc8ed5fee4f6","tid":1342930,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:21:40.000Z","msg":"上環係咪散晒啦？"},{"pid":"26e0ad5bd9682ee7898e036be0d2eb71adc5bbd8","tid":1342930,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:21:46.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ca916b5210c81acd24efd2b711fe226f48493a86","tid":1342930,"uid":136971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cbcd05e944246416daed5cf5ef2484ba4fc14e","tid":1342930,"uid":272424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:22:16.000Z","msg":"睇咗幾個鐘 靜晒"},{"pid":"0b4a2e1aa5cc74d5031c178b76df6d761367cefb","tid":1342930,"uid":141354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:22:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca83fd24afcc826601b476e1f38ae8cacd7081f9","tid":1342930,"uid":274854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:22:27.000Z","msg":"中環嘅就be water,撤啦"},{"pid":"de7c50082a9542109facd5c0ea06fc9bf32ef1eb","tid":1342930,"uid":189822,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:22:43.000Z","